OL,6,FThe inaugural match took place back in
OL,7,FFebruary when Everton's under-18s
OL,8,Ffaced their Wigan Athletic
OL,9,Fcounterparts, in front of 10,000
OL,10,Fspectators.
OL,12,FSince then there's been two further
OL,13,Ftest events at the at the newly-named
OL,14,FHill Dickinson Stadium, and the first
OL,15,Fcompetitive game is this weekend,
OL,16,FSaturday 23 August, as they face
OL,17,FBrighton
