OL,4,CPark to Bramley-Moore Dock
OL,6,FEverton's new home, situated at
OL,7,FBramley-Moore Dock in Vauxhall, is set
OL,8,Fto be the seventh-biggest stadium in
OL,9,Fthe Premier League, with a capacity of
OL,10,F52,888.
OL,12,FOnly Manchester City, Arsenal,
OL,13,FLiverpool, West Ham, Tottenham and
OL,14,FManchester United have larger grounds.
OL,16,FParts of the stadium will also feature
OL,17,Fsafe-standing seats.
