OL,6,FThe club has also confirmed that the
OL,7,Fground is "future-proofed", meaning it
OL,8,Fcan increase its capacity should the
OL,9,Fgovernment change the legislation
OL,10,Fsurrounding the ratio of one person
OL,11,Fstanding to one seat.
OL,13,FIn total, the project will give
OL,14,FEverton more than 13,000 extra seats
OL,15,Fwhen compared to Goodison Park.
