OL,4,CPark to Bramley-Moore Dock
OL,6,FThe initial cost of moving away from
OL,7,FGoodison Park was estimated to be
OL,8,Faround #500 million, but it is now
OL,9,Fbelieved to have cost closer to #800
OL,10,Fmillion, with the club enlisting the
OL,11,Fhelp of international banks, such as
OL,12,FJP Morgan, to finance the move.
OL,14,FThe true extent of the stadium's cost
OL,15,Fwas revealed in documents from
OL,16,FEverton's appeal to their 10-point
OL,17,Fdeduction in the 2023-24 season, due
OL,18,Fto a breach of the Profit and
OL,19,FSustainability Rules.
