OL,6,FWhat are Everton's plans for the new
OL,7,Fstadium?
OL,9,FThe Club moved into the Hill Dickinson
OL,10,Fin time for the 2025-26 Premier League
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FAfter three test events in the first
OL,14,Fhalf of 2025, the first competitive
OL,15,Ffixture featuring the first team is
OL,16,Fthe Brighton game on Saturday 23
OL,17,FAugust.
