OL,4,CPark to Bramley-Moore Dock
OL,6,FThe stadium has also been chosen as
OL,7,Fone of six English venues to host the
OL,8,F2028 European Championships, alongside
OL,9,FWembley, Tottenham Hotspur Stadium,
OL,10,FEtihad Stadium, St James' Park and
OL,11,FVilla Park.
OL,13,FAlongside the Euros, Everton's new
OL,14,Fstadium may also be used for the first
OL,15,FRugby League ashes in more than 20
OL,16,Fyears.
