OL,6,FFans are being told to plan ahead, as
OL,7,Fthe "real test awaits" for Merseyrail,
OL,8,Fahead of the Toffee's first league
OL,9,Fgame at their new stadium.
OL,11,FMerseyrail will be running a 15 minute
OL,12,Fservice on the Southport, Ormskirk,
OL,13,FHunts Cross and Headbolt Lane lines
OL,14,Fbefore and after the match, with a new
OL,15,Ffootbridge and fan management zone in
OL,16,Fplace to ease the flow of people
OL,17,Fcoming through the station.
